Class BikeTypeController

java.lang.Object
com.weatherAPI.weatherApplication.controller.BikeTypeController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/api/bike-types") @CrossOrigin(origins="http://localhost:3000") public class BikeTypeController extends Object
REST controller for managing bike type data. Provides endpoints to retrieve bike type details and availability by type.
